{"tid":925381,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"想識朋友就入黎啦-無限制吹水WhatsApp group","createTime":"2018-12-02T17:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T23:59:20.000Z","uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3cf54bb060045954adcd71bb288471a210f644c6","tid":925381,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T17:13:30.000Z","msg":"入過好多group 都發現識唔到人？<br />\n傾唔到偈？就算傾到偈都深交唔到？<br />\n我明呀，我真係明呀！<br />\n我地呢個group 打正旗號係識朋友嘅<br />\n<strong>吹水、吃喝玩樂、講心事、甚至人生哲理<br />\n只要你肯講，我就肯同你傾</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過入得黎當然有少少規則啦<br />\n<em>1）入黎為左宣傳業務就過主喇<br />\n2）發佈不良資訊係我大忌，必定移除<br />\n3）唔係話唔俾你溝女，不過俾人投訴我當騷擾處理。</em><br />\n<br />\n睇完都覺得自己適合嘅，就填form加入啦<br />\nAdmin大概會一星期加一次人，盡量以男女平衡為原則<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/n4W7lcrqepGHaxw23\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2Fn4W7lcrqepGHaxw23&d=1udu5iyFiETkxFLtB4NST%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=0cef95ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/n4W7lcrqepGHaxw23</a>"},{"pid":"61e335ee2410a544f319c76763e65c746594645a","tid":925381,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T18:55:50.000Z","msg":"睡前一推"},{"pid":"96aca896f5c4e7d0016dec806d9772bd1179c860","tid":925381,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:34:27.000Z","msg":"早晨一推"},{"pid":"3046fc22e7709cf834e069b24e7919061c610bc1","tid":925381,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:07:29.000Z","msg":"下午一推"},{"pid":"b7235208c20b92ce8c11158dd4e5f0b2acb7faaf","tid":925381,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:22:17.000Z","msg":"黃昏一推"},{"pid":"ece1bf588d421ffadec38aa075dc49681cc415bb","tid":925381,"uid":86246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:22:48.000Z","msg":"呢d gp最尾都係變小圈子gp"},{"pid":"a5d5f733dd1900661b4d843b01905e3929dd2e48","tid":925381,"uid":120980,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:31:47.000Z","msg":"呢種group大多數都係一開頭加入果陣會有三兩個主動say hi同叫你自我介紹<br />\n<br />\n講完一輪之後任你點樣出聲啲人都係當你冇到<br />\n<br />\n佢地有佢地圍內繼續小圍子<br />\n<br />\n你有你自己繼續同空氣講嘢"},{"pid":"e9d7bc69e327064d12da447b5a9de00b42673685","tid":925381,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T12:33:44.000Z","msg":"首先，所有人我一開始都係唔識嘅，唔存在小圈子問題。<br />\n其次，我有幾個熟嘅朋友都係玩group 識返黎，我又唔會好似你咁悲觀。<br />\n當然，如果你本身都係傾向小圈子嘅，唔怪得你咁諗嘅。"},{"pid":"ed86775883887cf437613570c944d245244e0f81","tid":925381,"uid":90461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000b5154c06220293ff0ff4cc4598173c4806c51","tid":925381,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T00:33:55.000Z","msg":"今晚加人"},{"pid":"06cf733a05b277f52080695b058886584e451e23","tid":925381,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:01:49.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"aa274e73c042be3bfbe6416d1beab152b50779b4","tid":925381,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ece1bf588d421ffadec38aa075dc49681cc415bb","tid":925381,"uid":86246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:22:48.000Z","msg":"呢d gp最尾都係變小圈子gp"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:04:30.000Z","msg":"依D gp係填完之後見你係仔就已經唔add你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3e16a0ff2512020ded67620f653d47b909d2fa","tid":925381,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:11:15.000Z","msg":"小人之心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係都要覺得人為搵食同溝女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b93125bd1a7bb9fd387fdea4b055bddc417d14","tid":925381,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"cbad0eeefd224a83851822dbb25ae3eb83c568d9","tid